    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="custom-quote warning"><span class="custom-quote-svg"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" data-reactroot=""><path fill="" d="M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z" undefined="1"></path><path stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2" stroke="" d="M12 8V13"></path><path stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2" stroke="" d="M12 15.99V16.01"></path></svg></span><p class="custom-quote-title">注意</p><p>写于2022年7月15日</p></div><h2 id="1-node-js的安装及环境配置"><a href="#1-node-js的安装及环境配置" class="headerlink" title="1 node js的安装及环境配置"></a>1 node js的安装及环境配置</h2><p>（由Ryan Dahl开发，是一个基于<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/Chrome/5633839">Chrome</a> <a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/V8/6178125">V8</a>引擎的<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/JavaScript/321142">JavaScript</a>运行环境，</p><p>使用了一个<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8/9597519">事件驱动</a>、非阻塞式I&#x2F;O模型，让JavaScript 运行在<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%AB%AF/6492316">服务端</a>的开发平台，</p><p>它让JavaScript成为与<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/PHP/9337">PHP</a> <a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/Python/407313">Python</a> <a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/Perl/851577">Perl</a>、<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/Ruby/11419">Ruby</a>等服务端语言平起平坐的<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/1379708">脚本语言</a></p><details class="custom-details"><summary><strong>node 安装过程截图</strong></summary><p><img src="http://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/node.jpg" alt="1"></p><p><img src="http://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/node4.png" alt="2"></p><p><img src="http://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/node5.png" alt="3"></p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/node5-1.jpg" alt="4"></p></details><p>其实就是无脑下一步，选择目录的时候要注意一下就行了。</p><h3 id="1-1-测试是否安装成功"><a href="#1-1-测试是否安装成功" class="headerlink" title="1.1 测试是否安装成功"></a>1.1 测试是否安装成功</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">node</span> -v<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> -v<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://shoot.photo/images/2022/07/20/PKWu5.png" alt="1"></p><p>解决npm查询不到版本号，方法一：<a href="https://past-taleggio-288.notion.site/node-24b6cf34d5c24186b7ef1ea7028b7fda">https://past-taleggio-288.notion.site/node-24b6cf34d5c24186b7ef1ea7028b7fda</a></p><h3 id="1-2-配置环境变量"><a href="#1-2-配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="1.2 配置环境变量"></a>1.2 配置环境变量</h3><details class="custom-details"><summary><strong>配置环境过程</strong></summary><p><p>在刚才安装nodejs的根目录下，创建node_global，node_cache文件夹</p><p><img src="https://shoot.photo/images/2022/07/20/PKaAn.png"></p><p>以管理员身份-打开cmd，配置路径</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> config <span class="token builtin class-name">set</span> prefix <span class="token string">"E:\develop<span class="token entity" title="\n">\n</span>odejs<span class="token entity" title="\n">\n</span>ode_global"</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> config <span class="token builtin class-name">set</span> cache <span class="token string">"E:\develop<span class="token entity" title="\n">\n</span>odejs<span class="token entity" title="\n">\n</span>ode_cache"</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>修改全局路径 node_global</p><p>修改缓存路径 node_cache<br>“”内路径需要根据自己实际情况来进行修改</p><p>注意：修改全局安装路径后，需要在系统环境变量Path中添加该路径，否则之后使用npm install –global xxx，xxx都报错找不到命令。</p><hr><li><strong>找到电脑环境配置</strong></li><p>win10&amp;win11：右键此电脑-属性-高级系统设置-高级-环境变量</p><p>win11还可以：点设置-系统-关于-高级系统设置-高级-环境变量</p><p><img src="http://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/node.png"></p><p>完成以上操作后，在<strong>用户变量</strong>中创建NODE_PATH变量，变量值为node_modeules路径地址</p><p><img src="https://shoot.photo/images/2022/07/20/PKmy7.png"></p><p>在<strong>系统变量</strong>中选择Path添加如下属性：<br><img src="https://shoot.photo/images/2022/07/20/PKbOK.png"></p></p></details><h2 id="2-安装git"><a href="#2-安装git" class="headerlink" title="2 安装git"></a>2 安装git</h2><p>官网<a href="https://git-scm.com/">https://git-scm.com/</a></p><p>找到首页下方的Downloads</p><p>下载对应系统（MAC、Windows、Linux&#x2F;Unix）安装包</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/1.png"></p><details class="custom-details"><summary><strong>安装git过程</strong></summary><p>找到下载的安装包（我下载的是windows系统的Git-2.34.1-64-bit.exe ），双击打开点击Next</p><p><strong>选择安装组件</strong></p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/3.png"></p><p>各个组件勾选含义 ：</p><p>√  Additional icons On the Desktop:桌面添加图标</p><p>√  Windows Explorer integration Git Bash Here&#x2F;Git GUI here:在windows资源管理器里集成Git Bash和Git GUI</p><p>√  Git LFS（Large File Support）:Git大文件支持</p><p>√  Associate .git* configuration files with the default text editor:将 .git* 配置文件与默认文本编辑器关联</p><p>√  Associate .sh files to be run with Bash:关联要与 Bash 运行的 .sh 文件</p><p>√  Check daily for Git for Windows updates:每日检查Windows版本的Git更新</p><p>√  (NEW!)Add a Git Bash Profile to Windows Terminal:将Git Bash的配置文件添加在Windows终端中的配置文件中（这是2.34.1版本新增的功能，省去了自己额外单独添加）</p><p>可以按照上述截图进行勾选，也可以自己根据组件含义进行勾选自己需要的组件，之后点击Next。</p><hr><p><strong>调整新存储库中初始分支的名称</strong></p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/4.png"><br>选择区别：</p><p>√  Let Git Decide:桌Git自己决定，当前默认是master。</p><p>√  Override the default branch name for new repositories:自己填写默认分支，常用的有”main”、”truck”、”development”，在这里我选择main</p><p>可以根据自己喜好选择初始名字，之后点击Next。</p><hr><p><strong>选择ssh可执行文件</strong></p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/5.png"></p><hr><p><strong>选择’git pull’的默认行为</strong></p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/6.png"></p><p>行为介绍：</p><p>√ Default:快进或者合并。</p><p>√ Rebase:变基。</p><p>√ Only ever fast-forward:只有快进。</p><p>这个选择默认就行，之后点击 Next。</p><hr><p><strong>配置实验选项</strong></p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/7.png"></p><p>正在开发的功能，小白不建议选择，之后点击Next。</p><p>之后就等待安装完成就行了</p><hr></details><h2 id="3-hexo-下载"><a href="#3-hexo-下载" class="headerlink" title="3 hexo 下载"></a>3 hexo 下载</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-cli -g <span class="token comment">#安装hexo</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="4-检查安装"><a href="#4-检查安装" class="headerlink" title="4 检查安装"></a>4 检查安装</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">node</span> -v<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> -v<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">git</span> --version<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo -v<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><hr><p><strong>安装成功效果</strong></p><p><img src="https://shoot.photo/images/2022/07/18/P1jSp.jpg"></p><hr><h2 id="5-创建仓库及配置SSH连接"><a href="#5-创建仓库及配置SSH连接" class="headerlink" title="5 创建仓库及配置SSH连接"></a>5 创建仓库及配置SSH连接</h2><h3 id="5-1-创建github仓库"><a href="#5-1-创建github仓库" class="headerlink" title="5.1 创建github仓库"></a>5.1 创建github仓库</h3><p>利用github仓库，存放静态网站资源，达到挂载网站的目的<br><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712130507904.bmp"></p><p>需要注意的是作为网站访问的这个仓库，仓库名称一定是，<strong>拥有者名+github.io</strong></p><hr><h3 id="5-2-生成ssh-keys"><a href="#5-2-生成ssh-keys" class="headerlink" title="5.2 生成ssh keys"></a>5.2 生成ssh keys</h3><p>在博客文件夹根目录下，右键，<br>调用git bash here功能<br><img src="https://shoot.photo/images/2022/07/18/P11QR.jpg"></p><p>先输入<code>ssh</code><br>查看是否已经安装ssh，git默认有安装</p><hr><p>本地生成ssh keys</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “邮箱地址”<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/a.png"></p><hr><li><strong>在本地电脑中找到.ssh文件夹</strong></li><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712133709772.bmp"></p><p>一般默认都是，c\Users\用户名.ssh</p><p>找到秘钥的位置，并用记事本打开，复制其内容(ctrl+a全选，ctrl+c复制，ctrl+v粘贴)</p><hr><p>打开github，头像箭头，下拉选项setting（设置）-SSH与GPG keys -new ssh keys（新建ssh秘钥）</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712144700233.bmp"></p><p>把在本地生成的秘钥内容粘贴至此秘钥处，标题可以随便取。</p><hr><p>为了后面流程，在github里顺便设置person access tokens（个人访问令牌）</p><p>(与ssh选项同一列，下面选择Developer setting log  -Generate new token)</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712160103385.bmp"></p><p>下面勾选权限，建议全部勾选</p><p>点击生成，生成的序列号，<strong>要复制下来在存在本地，他只显示一次，如果忘记了，还需要重新生成一次</strong>。</p><hr><p>测试ssh是否绑定成功（在git里操作）</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">ssh</span> -T git@github.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/c.png"><br>如果问你（yes or no），直接yes就可以得到上面这段话</p><hr><h2 id="6-搭建本地博客"><a href="#6-搭建本地博客" class="headerlink" title="6 搭建本地博客"></a>6 搭建本地博客</h2><p>创建一个放置博客文件夹的文件，在里面启用git Bash here</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/d.png"></p><li><strong>初始化hexo</strong></li><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo init<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/123.png"></p><li><strong>生成hexo本地页面</strong></li><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo s<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/675.png"></p><hr><p>浏览器复制粘贴该地址，即可访问本地搭建的博客<br><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/731.png"></p><hr><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo clean： <span class="token comment">#清理编译文件</span>hexo g：<span class="token comment">#编译项目</span>hexo s<span class="token punctuation">(</span>server<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> <span class="token comment">#本地预览运行项目</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><hr><h2 id="7-上传至本地博客至GitHub"><a href="#7-上传至本地博客至GitHub" class="headerlink" title="7 上传至本地博客至GitHub"></a>7 上传至本地博客至GitHub</h2><h3 id="7-1-修改配置文件"><a href="#7-1-修改配置文件" class="headerlink" title="7.1 修改配置文件"></a>7.1 修改配置文件</h3><p>在创建博客文件夹的根目录下修改-config.yml文件</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/432.png"></p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/abc.png"></p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">deploy:  type: <span class="token function">git</span>  repository: 你的github地址  branch: main<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><hr><h3 id="7-2-安装hexo-deployer-git-自动部署发布工具"><a href="#7-2-安装hexo-deployer-git-自动部署发布工具" class="headerlink" title="7.2 安装hexo-deployer-git 自动部署发布工具"></a>7.2 安装hexo-deployer-git 自动部署发布工具</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-deployer-git --save <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/d1.png"></p><h3 id="7-3-编译文件生成页面"><a href="#7-3-编译文件生成页面" class="headerlink" title="7.3 编译文件生成页面"></a>7.3 编译文件生成页面</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo g<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712153507301.bmp"></p><h3 id="7-4-本地文件上传到Github"><a href="#7-4-本地文件上传到Github" class="headerlink" title="7.4 本地文件上传到Github"></a>7.4 本地文件上传到Github</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo d<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/d5.png"></p><hr><p><strong>特别注意</strong>在上传时，浏览器会跳出关于github的验证,要耐心等候</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220711114554336.bmp"></p><p>输入用户名</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712154223503.bmp"></p><p>输入令牌</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712154251911.bmp"></p><p>(就是在github生成的那个，切记要保存)</p><hr><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/987.png"></p><p>成功后</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712160740179.bmp"></p><p>可以直接访问仓库名如，sxlz-jack.github.io</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/aa2f760148fbcbf6c3ce0b43cbe3433c.png"></p><hr><h2 id="8-安装Aurora主题"><a href="#8-安装Aurora主题" class="headerlink" title="8 安装Aurora主题"></a>8 安装Aurora主题</h2><details class="custom-details"><summary><strong>安装Aurora主题过程</strong></summary><p><h3 id="8-1-配置"><a href="#8-1-配置" class="headerlink" title="8.1 配置"></a><li>8.1 配置</li></h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-theme-aurora --save <span class="token comment">#进入hexo初始化目录用git执行</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712162012944.bmp"></p><hr><p>因为主题是使用 NPM 或者 Yarn 安装的，而不是 clone 到 themes 文件夹的。所以我们需要自己创建一个配置文件。你只需要在 Hexo 博客的根目录下创建一个_config.aurora.yml 配置文件来配置主题</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712162340361.bmp"></p><p>此时打开配置文件发现是空的我们可以到node_modules下找到hexo-theme-aurora</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712162534967.bmp"></p><h3 id="8-2-修改配置"><a href="#8-2-修改配置" class="headerlink" title="8.2 修改配置"></a><li>8.2 修改配置</li></h3><p>打开_comfig.yml</p><p>由默认主题改为Aurora<br><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712164111123.bmp"></p><hr><p>由于Aurora是vue3项目</p><p>打开根目录下的_config.yml</p><p>修改路由方式</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/12380.png"></p><p>运行</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo clean <span class="token operator">&amp;</span> hexo g <span class="token operator">&amp;</span> hexo server<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712163741994.bmp"></p><hr><h3 id="8-3-上传并覆盖GitHub仓库"><a href="#8-3-上传并覆盖GitHub仓库" class="headerlink" title="8.3 上传并覆盖GitHub仓库"></a><li>8.3 上传并覆盖GitHub仓库</li></h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo d<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/capture_20220712164332037.bmp"></p><p>打开仓库地址  主题配置成功</p><p><img src="https://www.sxlz.club/wp-content/themes/sakura-3.x/manifest/forin/20220214153036.png"></p></p></details><h2 id="9-参考教程"><a href="#9-参考教程" class="headerlink" title="9 参考教程"></a>9 参考教程</h2><p>Aurora主题安装: <a href="https://blog.nicely.fun/post/Hexo-Aurora-Cos-CDN">https://blog.nicely.fun/post/Hexo-Aurora-Cos-CDN</a></p><p>hexo+github搭建个人博客：<a href="https://wushishu.xyz/post/be8880ea.html">https://wushishu.xyz/post/be8880ea.html</a></p><p>保姆级hexo+github搭建个人博客：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1mU4y1j72n?p=1&vd_source=6e1e9ccd3b56d44ab6e49e2b16537391">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1mU4y1j72n?p=1&vd_source&#x3D;6e1e9ccd3b56d44ab6e49e2b16537391</a></p><p>github怎么绑定自己的域名：<a href="https://www.likecs.com/show-30474.html">https://www.likecs.com/show-30474.html</a></p><p>博客搭建日志：<a href="https://dhndzwxj.vercel.app/3276806131.html">https://dhndzwxj.vercel.app/3276806131.html</a></p><p>主题官方文档：<a href="https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/zh/guide/getting-started.html#%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83">https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/zh/guide/getting-started.html#%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
